        >
          <h2
            class="av3-h2"
          >
            <button
              class="av3-heading-btn"
              type="button"
            >
              Attention routes information
            </button>
          </h2>
          <span
            class="av3-section-role"
          >
            Mechanism
          </span>
        </div>
        <p
          class="av3-section-outcome"
        >
          You can describe what Q, K, and V each do.
        </p>
        <button
          class="av3-paragraph av3-paragraph--grounded"
